</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_278" id="139r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l1">VVir ~ die <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des Rats etc
                                <expan>Bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / daʒ für vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l2">kumen ſein die
                            <expan>hernachgeſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> . <del rend="strikethrough"> vvie Jr </del>
                        vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l3"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns
                                <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> / vvie Jn der Edell
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . her Eberhart
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l4">cʒu Eppenſtein aufgehalten het .
                                <expan>Mitname<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>heinrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Rumell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l5">dreẏ pallen wılhelm Ebner . ij Sewme . Hanſen kerner
                        auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l6">ij ſewme . vnd dem Eẏtell Jacob j Saum gevvancʒ / die
                        Er Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l7"><expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab / Als vns die
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> geſagt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l8">gebeten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Daʒ vvir
                        darümb des <expan>vorge<ex>nante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Eberhart<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l9"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu Eppenſtein freunde
                        vverden <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd alſo werden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l10">vvir <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Eberhart<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu Eppenſtein vnd aller
                                <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l11">helffer vnd diener vnd auch aller der die darunter
                        verdaht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l12">ſein gut freunde v̈mb die tat ongeuerde . Mit vrkund
                        dicʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l13">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan></del>
<expan>Geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> am freytag vor <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        Suntag Letare in der <expan>vaſte<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_278" id="139r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des rats etc.,
                                <expan>bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., daz für uns kumen sein die
                                <expan>hernachgeschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                                <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>, wie in der edell
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> her Eberhart,
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> czu Eppenstein, aufgehalten het
                                <expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Rumell drey pallen, Wilhelm Ebner ii
                        sewme, Hansen Kerner auch ii sewme und dem Eytell Jacob i saum gewancz, die
                        er in <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab, als uns die
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> gesagt und gebeten
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> daz wir darümb des
                                <expan>vorge<ex>nante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Eberhart<ex>en,</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu Eppenstein, freunde werden
                                <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und also werden wir
                                <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Eberhart<ex>en,</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu Eppenstein, und aller
                                <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> helffer und diener und auch aller,
                        der die darunter verdaht sein, gut freunde ümb die tat, on geverde. Mit
                        urkund dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> etc.
                            <expan>Geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> am freytag vor <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        suntag letare in der <expan>vaste<ex>n.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
